{"tid":2029172,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我老細聽到立國安法嚇傻左","createTime":"2020-05-22T06:18:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T07:26:00.000Z","uid":5133,"like":29,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7157271a86c3eaf813766bc418aaf64c337316d4","tid":2029172,"uid":5133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:18:36.000Z","msg":"睇到港版國安法個標題嚇到叫左出黎，老細問咩事，我照讀比佢聽，讀左標題內文都未開始讀， <br />\n<br />\n佢成塊面白哂，自言自語，猛咁話「共慘黨殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生， <br />\n<br />\n共慘黨殺到黎，香港九龍新界無得避，要化身玉皇大帝打救蒼生&hellip;&hellip;」 <br />\n<br />\n跟住衝左上天台，叫左一聲&quot;鳴呀，點解係我&quot;就跳左落去，成班同事追上去都追唔切， <br />\n<br />\n有兩個女同事嚇到暈左，仲有個男同事當場嚇到幾左弱智，不停問人要唔要食腸仔蛋。 <br />\n<br />\n我就好好彩無咩事，但同班同事五十幾個人即時變左失業，你條仆街真係害人害物&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"709acc3c247521680e0df22e97789d2354bc0344","tid":2029172,"uid":192465,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:23:37.000Z","msg":"已閱。上一頁。"},{"pid":"fcfef2ec40eb959ee54c2ab1e548664d2cca90d9","tid":2029172,"uid":200861,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:26:34.000Z","msg":"估唔到呢篇潮文咁快就變成現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee4b399d3c8c346862520d85204aeaea76291779","tid":2029172,"uid":65298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"709acc3c247521680e0df22e97789d2354bc0344","tid":2029172,"uid":192465,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:23:37.000Z","msg":"已閱。上一頁。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:45:02.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"a9ee14b2aa4a7a92d266f1c2638fc09bd14fecbf","tid":2029172,"uid":11694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcfef2ec40eb959ee54c2ab1e548664d2cca90d9","tid":2029172,"uid":200861,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:26:34.000Z","msg":"估唔到呢篇潮文咁快就變成現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:50:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/a